<h2>About ShushaIMUN</h2>

<p style="text-align:center;font-size:18px;max-width:900px;margin:auto;">
ShushaIMUN is an international Model United Nations conference where students strengthen their leadership, diplomacy, negotiation and public speaking skills while discussing today's most important global issues. Our mission is to inspire the next generation of leaders through meaningful debate and international cooperation.
</p>

